This directory vendors and adapts a subset of KernelPatch's arm64 hook core.

Upstream project:
- https://github.com/bmax121/KernelPatch

Source basis:
- kernel/include/hook.h
- kernel/base/hook.c

Upstream license:
- GPL-2.0-or-later

The copied code in this directory retains upstream copyright notices.
Local adaptations remove KernelPatch-specific runtime integration and keep
only the low-level arm64 branch/trampoline/relocation logic needed by
`debugger_linux_lkm`.
